{"tid":1239892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠成個記招根本冇料到","createTime":"2019-06-18T08:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:10:42.000Z","uid":212626,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ec1a724aaeb2f946f6ccf87ff33715d6883e7d","tid":1239892,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"完全冇回應到五大訴求<br />\n「撤回」兩隻字死都唔肯講<br />\n暴動論亦冇撤回<br />\n更加唔使講撤消控罪同下台<br />\n淨係不斷重複講自己有反省、玩文字遊戲<br />\n我想問佢，你究竟反省咗啲乜<br />\n咁多人反對同上街抗爭<br />\n就只係因為個條例修訂或政府工作有「不足」咁簡單？<br />\n<br />\n佢今次成功向世界展示同證明香港並不存在民主社會<br />\n政府無視市民訴求，市民嘅意見，左耳入、右耳出<br />\n只要單方面覺得個政策對香港好就得<br />\n人地南韓二百萬人上街，令朴槿惠下台、政府重組<br />\n我地香港呢？ Sorry lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主？ 我呸"},{"pid":"1466344b3054188b96bbb757e8a32e80953a7c21","tid":1239892,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"民陣好快啲入紙申請不反對通知書<br />\n佢唔撤我地每個禮拜日都出黎遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4895978674a0268fa08f8a251a2a3acee3f71ae8","tid":1239892,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ed1dae93f6047939d9918353fd9bce11e80970","tid":1239892,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"Btw 記得登記做選民"},{"pid":"f4ec078185c0333886ea96d70406fedbb27ea13c","tid":1239892,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c5ef66605d75122009fdccdbb7e966ad817e0a22","tid":1239892,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2afc79827965cdf